\p
\v 1 Piak m…®n…ô m…®ne nowin…®k m…®n…ô, yaksorkeikei m…ô takharkun m…ô nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô apa Masedonia kw…ôshajoun m…ô Kughen ramaut…ô-p…ôn k…®n kafan n…®huv…ôyen k…®mi …ôri…ô.\x - \xo 8:1 \xt Rom 15:26; 2 Kor 9:1-2 \x*  
\v 2 Iri…ô k…®m…®sar…ô pawk ye n…ômh…ôyen ehu…ô k…®rik, kap…ôri…ô naut…ô r…®rk…ôk, m…ôr…®g n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô rukwar huv…ô k…®n nagienien, ror p…ôn kamhav…ôh-si-p…ôn mane ehu…ô k…®mi n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n.  
\v 3 Yakamni-…ôrhav pre tuk …ômi…ô m…ô iri…ô k…®mnhav…ôhsi-p…ôn mane ehu…ô, rapita yame r…®kiri…ô r…ôs…®k m…ô tukpihav…ôh-si p…ôn. Kamhav…ôhsi-…ôhrav r…ômhen k…®n yame n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô ramuh,  
\v 4 m…®saiyoh …ômaw…ô m-r…®psaah m…ô k…®maw…ô jakseighan k…®n …ôri…ô p…ôh iri…ô tuksasitu ye wok kape n…®w…ôh-sip…ônien mane k…®mi narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô apa Jerusalem.  
\v 5 Yakhap…ôh nharkunien m…ô iri…ô tuksasitu rehu…ô m…ôknak…®n, m…ôr…®g iri…ô k…®sasitu. K…®m…®s…ôkup…ôn mhav…ôhsi-p…ôn n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô k…®mi Yermaru. Kwas…®g ik…®n, khav…ôhsi-p…ôn n…®mraghien kap…ôri…ô k…®mi …ômaw…ô r…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô n…ôr…®gien kape Kughen.   
\p
\v 6 K…®ni kup…ôn, Taetas a in r…®mnamk…®r …ômi…ô tuk narukien k…®n mane kape nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô; ror p…ôn, yaks…ôkeikei k…®min m…ô in tukram…ôkeikei mam…ôm…®r k…®mi…ô min meriaji taksaruk fam k…®n mane yame takhav…ôhsi-…ôrhav.  
\v 7 Ye nar…®mnar m…®fam e, k…®mi…ô nakasor rhuv…ô p…®k mapita, in e, nhat…ôt…ôyen kap…ômi…ô, m…®ne n…ôgkiarien kap…ômi…ô, m…®ne n…®rkunien kap…ômi…ô, m…®ne n…ôrer-t…®mt…®mien kap…ômi…ô, m…®ne norkeikeiyen kap…ômi…ô tuk …ômaw…ô. K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, yakorkeikei m…ô taksaruk…®n mane m…ôknak…®n ye norien yame rhuv…ô rapita.   
\p
\v 8 Pa r…®m…ô yakam…ôkeikei k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô taksor. M…ôr…®g y…®mnhajoun …ômi…ô m…ô n…ôm…ô tan…ô p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n…ô r…®kiri…ô ragien tuk nasituyen ye wok a. K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, yakm…ô jak…ôm-ru m…ô norkeikeiyen kap…ômi…ô in n…ôfrak…®sien r…ômhen k…®n …ôri…ô, u…ô n…®kam.  
\v 9 K…®mi…ô nakharkun huv…ô m…ô Yesu Kristo Yermaru kap…ôtaw…ô ramaut…ô-pre k…®n n…®huv…ôyen kafan k…®mi …ômi…ô. Kafan n…ôsan…®nien rehu…ô pawk, m…ôr…®g r…®mau…ô m…ô tukrasitu ir…ômi…ô, mor In m…ô kafan n…ôsan…®nien r…®rk…ôk. In r…®mau…ô mor In m…ô kafan nar k…®rik r…®rk…ôk ye tokrei tan…ô m…ô k…®mi…ô takhau…ô narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô, kap…ômi…ô nar…®mnar tukr…®psaah ye rao ye neai.\x - \xo 8:9 \xt Mat 8:20; Fil 2:6-7 \x*   
\p
\v 10 Jak…ôvhaag k…®mi …ômi…ô ye norien yame ratuatuk m…ô taksor. Ye newk yame ruau…ô muav…ôn, k…®mi…ô n…®m…®sokup…ôn m…®sorkeikei m…ô taksaruk…®n mane kape nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô, k…®ni k…®mi…ô m…®n n…®m…®sokup…ôn m…®saruk…®n mane.  
\v 11 Takt…ôkun ai, taksaruk…®n mane m…ô takseri…ôji n…®prai mane yame n…®m…®sorkeikei m…ô takhav…ôhsi-…ôrhav.  
\v 12 In nar apnap…®g m…ô kap…ômi…ô nar…®mnar r…®psaah u…ô r…®k…ôsk…ôh. Kughen, r…®kin tukragien tuk …ômi…ô tukm…ô nakhav…ôh-si p…ôn yerkimi…ô m…®fam.\x - \xo 8:12 \xt Mak 12:43-44 \x*   
\p
\v 13 Yakp…ôh norkeikeiyen m…ô n…®p…®g takhav…ôhsi-p…ôn mane ehu…ô k…®mi nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô, kwas…®g ik…®n, naks…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®n mane. M…ôr…®g ratuatuk …ôm…ô  
\v 14 m…ô taksasitu ye nim…ôhuak yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôkwakw…ô k…®n nar…®mnar, meinai kap…ômi…ô nar…®mnar r…®psaah. K…®ni n…®p…®g k…®rik, tukm…ô naks…ôkwakw…ô k…®n nar k…®rik, iri…ô tukharkun n…®sasituyen ir…ômi…ô. Norien a takasor, tukas…ôm n…ômhen.  
\v 15 R…ôri-p…ôn …ôm…ô N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen yame ramni m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúNarmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhav…ôh pawk n…ôv…®g…®nien rehu…ô, tukr…ômhen k…®n …ôri…ô; to r…®p…ôh napitayen.  
\q2 M…®ne narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhav…ôh pawk n…ôv…®g…®nien r…ôk…ôsk…ôh, tukhap…ôh n…®sakw…ôkw…ôyen k…®n n…ôv…®g…®nien.‚Äù\rq (Eks 16:18)\rq*   
\s1 Taetas ramv…ôn apa Korin  
\p
\v 16 Yakamni vi vi Kughen m…ô ramor r…®ki Taetas ramagien m…ô tukrasitu ir…ômi…ô, r…ômhen k…®n kafak n…ôr…®gien.  
\v 17 Y…®mnhani-p…ôn tuk Taetas m…ô tukrur…ô m…ôm …ômi…ô; k…®ni r…®kin ragien tuk norien n…ôgkiarien kap…ômaw…ô. M…ôr…®g in m…®n, r…®kin ragien m…®n tuk nur…ôyen masitu ir…ômi…ô. Ye n…ôr…®gien …ôm…ô kafan r…®mnorkeikei m…ô tukrur…ô m…ôm …ômi…ô.  
\v 18 K…®ni k…®maw…ô yaksher-pre m…®n k…®n piautaw…ô k…®rik raur…ô iriu min. Kw…ôn a, n…ôm…ôhuak m…®n…ô kamhasiai in tuk kafan wok tuk n…®ni-…ôrhavyen N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô.  
\v 19 K…®ni nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô k…®mnharpen in m…ô tukram…ôriw…ôk k…®maw…ô min n…®p…®g yakhav…ôhsi-…ôrhav mane yame n…®m…®saruk…®n. Yakhav…ôhsi-p…ôn mane k…®mi nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô m…ô jakshajoun m…ô r…®kimaw…ô ragien p…®k tuk nasituyen, m…®ne tuk n…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ôyen Kughen.  
\v 20 Yaksarkut m…ô yermam…ô k…®rik r…®k…ôk yame to r…®ni hah …ômaw…ô tuk norien kap…ômaw…ô tuk n…ôwhaiyen mane.  
\v 21 Ror m…ôkneik…®n meinai, yaksarkut m…ô jaksor nar…®mnar yame ratuatuk ye n…®mr…® Kughen m…®ne ye n…®mr…® narmam…ô.   
\p
\v 22 K…®ni yaksher-pre m…®n k…®n piautaw…ô k…®rik in tukr…®kwas…®g k…®n Taetas m…®ne in k…®rik. Y…®mnharkun m…ô kw…ôn a rorkeikei p…®k m…ô tukrasitu ye norien r…®psaah m…®ne ye wok r…®psaah. K…®ni takt…ôkun ai in rorkeikei p…®k m…ô tukrasitu ir…ômi…ô meinai in ramni n…ôfrak…®sien ir…ômi…ô.  
\v 23 K…®ni Taetas, k…®mru min yakawor wok k…®rikian…ô. K…®ni kw…ôn a r…®kwas…®g k…®n Taetas in m…®n ramor wok ye kwerkwan ir…ômi…ô, masitu ir…ômi…ô. M…®ne piautaw…ô mir k…®raru e, yame nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô k…®sher-p…ô k…®n …ôriu, kar…ôhsi-hakt…ô nhag Kristo.  
\v 24 Sor norkeikeiyen kap…ômi…ô r…®v…ôn tuk …ôris…®r, p…ôh nim…ôhuak m…®n…ô tuks…ôm, mharkun-ru m…ô rhawor e r…®kimaw…ô ramagien tuk …ômi…ô.\x - \xo 8:24 \xt 2 Kor 7:13-14 \x*   
\c 9  
\nb
\v 1 Yakpi-p…ôh nher-preyen k…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô e k…®mi …ômi…ô, r…®pihuv…ô …ôm…ô, meinai, nakw…ônharkun ta wok e kape nasituyen ye narmam…ô kape Kughen m…®n…ô apa Jerusalem.\x - \xo 9:1 \xt 2 Kor 8:1-7 \x*  
\v 2 Yakamni m…ôkneik…®n meinai yak…®rkun m…ô naksorkeikei m…ô taksasitu, k…®ni y…®mn…ôgn…ôg…®n ta …ômi…ô ye n…®mr…® n…ôm…ô Masedonia tukun, mamni m…®m…ô newk yame ruau…ô muav…ôn, k…®mi…ô apa Akaea n…®m…®s…ôrer matuk tuk n…®v…ôhsi-p…ônien mane. K…®ni n…®p…®g n…ôm…ôhuak apa Masedonia k…®m…®s…ôm m…ô r…®kimi…ô ragien p…®k tuk nasituyen, ramor m…®n …ôri…ô khapsaah kasorkeikei m…ô tuksasitu m…®n.  
\v 3 M…ôr…®g takt…ôkun ai, yakamher-pre k…®n piautaw…ô mis…®r e m…ô iris…®r tukrh…ôm …ômi…ô m…ô k…®mi…ô taksor nar yame n…®mnhani, r…ômhen k…®n yame yakw…ôni ta. K…®ni ror m…ôkneik…®n, kap…ômaw…ô n…ôgkiarien tuk n…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ôyen norien huv…ô kap…ômi…ô, p…ôh nien m…ô nar apnap…®g …ôm…ô.  
\v 4 M…ôr…®g tukm…ô nakhap…ôh n…®sorien, n…®p…®g jakur…ô k…®maw…ô n…ôm…ô Masedonia t…®ks…®n, k…®ni tuk…ôm m…ô k…®mi…ô nakhap…ôh n…®sor-…ôgk…ôpien, k…®ni taksaur…®s tukun, meinai k…®maw…ô yakw…ônhav…ôh-si hakt…ô ta nhagmi…ô. Tukror aur…®s …ômi…ô rapita.  
\v 5 Ror m…ôkneik…®n, r…®kik ram…ôs…®k m…ô jakam…ôkeikei maiyoh piautaw…ô mis…®r m…ô tukrhokup…ôn irak m…®rhur…ô m…®rh…ôm …ômi…ô p…ôh k…®s…ôm m…ô takhav…ôh-si-p…ôn mane yame nakw…ônhani ta m…ô taksaruk…®n. M…ôr…®g yakorkeikei m…ô takhav…ôh-si-p…ôn yerkimi…ô m-fam. P…ôh nien m…ô kam…ôkeikei k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô taksasitu.   
\s1 Norien kape n…ôwhaiyen nar…®mnar  
\p
\v 6 R…®kimi…ô tukram…ôs…®k n…ôgkiarien e: Yermam…ô yame ram…ôsim k…ôsk…ôh, tukr…®v…ôh n…ôv…®g…®nien iran r…®k…ôsk…ôh …ôm…ô. Yermam…ô yame ram…ôsim r…®psaah, tukr…®v…ôh n…ôsimien iran r…®psaah.\x - \xo 9:6 \xt Prov 11:24-25 \x*  
\v 7 K…®mi…ô k…®rikian…ô k…®rikian…ô takas…ôkeikei mhav…ôh-si-p…ôn naha nhag…®n yame rams…®-p…ôn yerkimi…ô m…ô takhav…ôh-si p…ôn. M…ôr…®g tukm…ô naksaruk k…®n mane meinai yermam…ô k…®rik ram…ôkeikei k…®mi…ô …ômi…ô tukun, r…®p…ôh natuatukien. Yakamni m…ôkneik…®n meinai Kughen rorkeikei yermam…ô yame rav…ôhsi-p…ôn yerkin m-fam.  
\v 8 K…®ni Kughen r…®rkun naut…ô-preyen k…®n n…®huv…ôyen m-fam kafan k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô tuk nar…®mnar fam ye n…®p…®g m-fam, takhav…ôh nar…®mnar fam yame naks…ôkwakw…ô k…®n, mhav…ôh m…®n r…ômhen m…ôkwakw m…ô taks…ôwhai.  
\v 9 Meinai N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ramni m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIn r…ôwhai kafan nar…®mnar r…®psaah k…®mi yav…ôn has m…®n…ô,  
\q2 k…®ni norien atuatuk kafan to r…®p…ôh n…®rk…ôkien.‚Äù\rq (Sam 112:9)\rq*   
\p
\v 10 K…®ni Kughen yame rav…ôhsi-p…ôn kweru nai k…®mi yem…ôsim, m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn m…®n n…ôv…®g…®nien nan, ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, In tukr…®v…ôh-si p…ôn nar…®mnar r…®psaah k…®mi …ômi…ô mor m…®n r…®psaah-…®psaah m…®n, m…ô k…®mi…ô takharkun n…®sasituyen ye narmam…ô t…®ks…®n m…®n. K…®ni tukror kw…ônkwan r…®psaah yame rams…®-p…ôn ye norien atuatuk kap…ômi…ô.\x - \xo 9:10 \xt Aes 55:10 \x*  
\v 11 Ye nar…®mnar fam ye n…®mraghien kap…ômi…ô, Kughen tukr…®v…ôh-si pre kafan n…®vhu…ôyen k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô k…®mi…ô takharkun n…ôwhaiyen n…®p…®g m…®fam. K…®ni n…®p…®g taksasitu, narmam…ô tukhani vi vi Kughen tukun.\x - \xo 9:11 \xt 2 Kor 1:11; 4:15 \x*   
\p
\v 12 Wok e yame nakasor, nakhav…ôhsi-p…ôn mane tuk n…ôv…®g…®nien ne narmam…ô kape Kughen yam…ô m…®ne n…®kumh…ô ram…ôs …ôri…ô, m…ôr…®g naksor nar huv…ô k…®rik rapita, in e narmam…ô khapsaah tuks…ôr…®g rhuv…ô, mhani vi vi Kughen tukun.  
\v 13 N…®p…®g naksor wok m…®n…ô a, narmam…ô kas…ôm norien kap…ômi…ô. K…®ni iri…ô tukhav…ôh-si hakt…ô nhag Kughen tukun, meinai k…®mi…ô nakasor …ôfrak…®s norien kape narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhani n…ôfrak…®sien ye N…ôvsaoyen Huv…ô kape Yesu Kristo. K…®ni iri…ô tukhav…ôh-si hakt…ô nhag Kughen meinai k…®mi…ô nakhav…ôhsi-p…ôn kap…ômi…ô mane ehu…ô k…®mi …ôri…ô m…®ne narmam…ô m…®fam.  
\v 14 K…®ni n…®p…®g iri…ô tuks…ôhuak tuk …ômi…ô, r…®kiri…ô tukram…ôs…®k …ômi…ô meinai Kughen r…®mnaut…ô-p…ôn k…®n kafan n…®huv…ôyen k…®mi …ômi…ô rapita, m…ô taksasitu p…®k ir…ôri…ô.  
\v 15 !P…ôh khani vi vi Kughen tuk T…®ni yame In r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ô k…®mi …ôtaw…ô! Nar e in e rhuv…ô rapita.   
\c 10  
\s1 Pol ramhorp…®n n…ôgkiarien kape narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhani hah in mham…ô kafan norien ror k…®raru  
\p
\v 1 Narmam…ô t…®ks…®n kamhani n…®kar…®k mham…ô kafak norien k…®raru. M…ô n…®p…®g k…®taw…ô-m k…®mi…ô, kafak n…ôr…®gien reiwaiyu …ôm…ô, m…ôr…®g n…®p…®g y…®mat…ôrhav m…ôp…ôh …ômi…ô, kafak norien r…®skai p…®k. M…ôr…®g yo Pol, yakam…ôkeikei k…®mi …ômi…ô tuk nar k…®rik, m…®m…ô Kristo, kafan n…ôr…®gien reiwaiyu, k…®ni In yem…ô mar.\x - \xo 10:1 \xt 1 Kor 2:3 \x* K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô,  
\v 2 yakamaiyoh …ômi…ô m…ô, taksor norien kap…ômi…ô ratuatuk m…ô n…®p…®g jakur…ô, m…®p…ôh n…ômien nar k…®rik m…ô to yak…ôgkiar skai pre k…®mi …ômi…ô tukun. M…ôr…®g yak…®rkun m…ô jakhek narmam…ô t…®ks…®n e yam…ô m…®ne kamhani m…ô yakam…ôri-p…ôn norien kape tokrei tan…ô,\x - \xo 10:2 \xt 1 Kor 4:21 \x*  
\v 3 meinai nar apnap…®g yaksar…ô ye tokrei tan…ô e, yakhap…ôh n…®sarowag…®nien ye norien yame narmam…ô kape tokrei tan…ô kasarowag…®n k…®n.  
\v 4 Ror m…ôkneik…®n meinai nar…®mnar kape narowag…®nien yame k…®maw…ô yakasarowag…®n k…®n, p…ôh nien m…ô nar…®mnar yame narmam…ô kape tokrei tan…ô kasarowag…®n k…®n. N…®kam. Nar…®mnar kap…ômaw…ô yame yakasarowagk…ôp k…®n, kamhav…ôh n…ôsan…®nien kape Kughen tuk noriahyen kw…ônmhan yame Setan ramerkwaig ik…®n.\x - \xo 10:4 \xt Efes 6:13-17 \x*  
\v 5 K…®maw…ô yaksoriah n…ôgkiarien eiku…ô m…®n…ô m…®ne n…ôr…®gien ausit m…®n…ô, iri…ô m-fam yame kas…ôrer …ôswas…®g k…®n narmam…ô tuk n…®rkunien Kughen. Yakhani-…ôhu n…ôt…ôr…®g-hasien m…®n…ô fam kape narmam…ô, m…®sor …ôri…ô kasarar ye n…ôr…®gien kap…ôri…ô masor n…ôkwai Kristo.  
\v 6 K…®ni n…®p…®g naks…ôri-p…ôn n…ôr…®gien kape Kristo, k…®mi…ô taks…ôrer matuk tuk n…®v…ôhsi-p…ônien narp…®nien k…®mi narmam…ô m-fam yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôs…®k n…ôkwan.   
\p
\v 7 !Ah! K…®mi…ô nakas…ôm nar kamor …ôrhav, m…ôr…®g nakseinein n…®pran. Tukm…ô yermam…ô k…®rik r…®rkun m…ô in yermam…ô k…®rik kape Kristo, tukram…ôkeikei m…®rkun huv…ô m…ô k…®maw…ô m…®n, narmam…ô kape Kristo r…ômhen k…®n in.  
\v 8 Tukm…ô ror n…®p…®g yakam…ôgkiar ye nehu…ôyen yame Yesu Yermaru r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ô k…®mi yo, yakam…ôgkiar ausit; m…ôr…®g to yakp…ôh naur…®sien tuk n…ôgkiar ausitien tukun, meinai Yesu r…®m…®w…ôhsi-p…ô nehu…ôyen k…®mi yo tuk n…®v…ôhsi-hakt…ôyen …ômi…ô, p…ôh nien m…ô tuk n…®v…ôhsi-…ôhuyen …ômi…ô.\x - \xo 10:8 \xt 2 Kor 13:10 \x*  
\v 9 Yakp…ôh norkeikeiyen m…ô r…®kimi…ô tukram…ôs…®k m…ô yakher-pre k…®n n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô e k…®mi …ômi…ô m…ô tukror …ômi…ô nakhag…®n.  
\v 10 M…ôr…®g narmam…ô t…®ks…®n kamhani n…®kar…®k mham…ô, ‚ÄúIn, kafan n…ôkw…ôkw…ô m…®n…ô khapam m…®sesr…ô, m…ôr…®g n…®p…®g in ramar…ô k…®taw…ô min, p…ôh nien m…ô in yermam…ô skai k…®rik, m…ôr…®g kafan n…ôgkiarien in nar apnap…®g …ôm…ô.‚Äù  
\v 11 Narmam…ô m…®n…ô a tukas…ôkeikei mharkun m…ô n…®p…®g jakur…ô k…®sar…ô k…®taw…ô-mir…ô, norien kafak tukr…ôut…ôn r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n yame kafak n…ôgkiarien in r…ôut…ôn ye n…ôkw…ôkw…ô yame yakamher-pre k…®n k…®mi …ômi…ô.   
\s1 Pol ramhorp…®n n…ôgkiarien kape narmam…ô yame kamhani mham…ô in p…ôh nien m…ô yemehu…ô kape nim…ôhuak apa Korin  
\p
\v 12 Narmam…ô t…®ks…®n kamhav…ôhsi-hakt…ô atuk …ôri…ô. Tukm…ô iri…ô yerp…®r…®g …ôfrak…®s rapita yo, to yakp…ôh n…ôgkiar-ausitien m…ô yo yerp…®r…®g r…ômhen k…®n …ôri…ô. M…ôr…®g, p…ôh nien m…ô iri…ô yerp…®r…®g …ôfrak…®s. Kas…ôkir …ômhen narmam…ô ye n…ôr…®gien …ôm…ô kap…ôri…ô, m…ô tuks…ôm m…ô norien kap…ôri…ô rhuv…ô u…ô rahas. Norien e yame kasor, r…ôt…ôwao.  
\v 13 M…ôr…®g k…®maw…ô yakhap…ôh n…®s…ôgkiar-ausitien rapita nehu…ôyen kap…ômaw…ô, m…ôr…®g yaks…ôgkiar ausit ye wok yame Kughen r…®mn…ôr…ôhu-p…ô m…ô kap…ômaw…ô, k…®ni wok e, k…®mi…ô m…®n apaik…®n.\x - \xo 10:13 \xt Rom 12:3 \x*  
