\v 9 K…®ni n…®p…®g k…®taw…ô k…®mnamhav…ôn, k…®ni kafak nar k…®rik r…®rk…ôk. Y…®m…®p…ôh naiyohyen nasituyen tuk yermam…ô k…®rik, meinai piautaw…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®mnhas…®-p…ôn Masedonia k…®mnhav…ôhsi-p…ô nar…®mnar yame y…®mn…ôkwakw…ô k…®n. Ror p…ôn, y…®m…®p…ôh naiyohyen …ômi…ô k…®n nar k…®rik, m…®p…ôh narkutien k…®mi …ômi…ô tuk narha-huv…ôyen tuk yo. Norien m…®n…ô a yakamor ye n…®p…®g m-fam.\x - \xo 11:9 \xt 2 Kor 12:13; Fil 4:15-16 \x*  
\v 10 Tukm…ô ror yakamausit tuk norien kafak, m…ôr…®g yermam…ô k…®rik apa Akaea to r…®p…ôh n…®niyen m…ô yakameiku…ô. N…ôgkiarien yame yakamni ram…ôfrak…®s r…ômhen …ôm…ô k…®n n…ôgkiarien yame Yesu Kristo ramni.  
\v 11 ?M…ôr…®g rhawor e y…®m…®p…ôh naiyohyen …ômi…ô k…®n nar k…®rik? P…ôh nien m…ô yak…ôm…ôk…®n …ômi…ô m…ôp…ôh naiyohyen k…®n nasituyen tuk …ômi…ô. N…®kam. Kughen r…®rkun m…ô yakorkeikei p…®k …ômi…ô.   
