\v 2 Yo yermam…ô k…®rik\f + \fr 12:2 \ft  Pol r…®p…ôh n…®niyen m…ô in atuk r…®mn…ôm n…ômr…ôrhavyen e. Ramni isok, mamni yermam…ô p…®s…®n. M…ôr…®g n…®p…®g kas…ôvhuek…®n p…ôpi…ô chapter 12, k…®taw…ô kharkun m…ô in ram…ôgkiar mamni atuk in.\f* yame yakamhat…ôt…ô ye Kristo. Kughen r…®v…ôh-ta yo muav…ôn ye rao ye neai\f + \fr 12:2 \ft  Gris ramni, ‚Äúheven namba tri‚Äù r…ômhen k…®n heven yame yerp…®r…®g p…®k. N…®pran ramni m…ô imei Kughen.\f*, newk fotin ruau…ô ta muav…ôn. Yakeinein m…ô n…®prak ruav…ôn u…ô nanm…®k …ôm…ô. Kughen …ôm…ô r…®rkun.  
\v 3 K…®ni mamni m…®n m…ô yakeinein m…ô n…®prak ruav…ôn u…ô nanm…®k …ôm…ô, m…ôr…®g yak…®rkun m…ô  
