\v 6 M…ôr…®g tukm…ô yakm…ô jakam…ôgkiar ausit, r…®p…ôh norien m…ô yo yarm…ôr, meinai n…ôgkiarien yame jak…ôgkiar ausit tukun in ram…ôfrak…®s. M…ôr…®g to yakp…ôh n…ôgkiar-ausitien m…ôkneik…®n, tam…ô narmam…ô khav…ôhsi-hakt…ô p…®k yo rapita ik…®n tukv…ôhsi-hakt…ô yo ik…®n. Yakorkeikei m…ô narmam…ô tuks…ôkir …ômhen yo ye n…ôgkiarien kafak m…®ne norien m…®n…ô kafak.   
\s1 N…ôsan…®nien kape Kughen r…®rkun n…®v…ôh-m…®raghien …ôtaw…ô  
\p
\v 7 Kughen r…®p…ôh norkeikeiyen m…ô jakausit tuk n…ôgkiarien vi yam…ô m…®ne In r…®mnor …ôpu k…®mi yo, k…®ni n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô a khahuv…ô m…®sapita. Ror p…ôn, In r…®mnher-p…ô k…®n n…ômh…ôyen ye n…®mraghien kafak r…ômhen k…®n nirh…® n…®m…®rh ramhai yo kape n…®p…®g m…®fam. N…ômh…ôyen a in r…ômhen k…®n y…ôgkiar k…®rik kape Setan yame ramor n…ômh…ôyen ye n…®prak, ramor yo yakp…ôh nausitien.\x - \xo 12:7 \xt Job 2:6 \x*  
\v 8 Y…®mn…ôkeikei k…®mi Yesu Yermaru m-k…®sis…ôr m…ô tukr…®r…ôhsi-ta n…ômh…ôyen a tuk yo.  
