\v 18 Y…®mn…ôkeikei k…®mi Taetas m…ô tukrur…ô tuk …ômi…ô, mher-pre k…®n piautaw…ô k…®rik iriu min. ?M…ôr…®g Taetas r…®mnor nar iko m…®v…ôh kap…ômi…ô nar…®mnar u…ô? N…®kam. Nakharkun m…ô kap…ômru n…ôt…ôr…®gien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, k…®ni yakawor norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô.\x - \xo 12:18 \xt 2 Kor 8:6,16-18 \x*   
\p
\v 19 P…ôh nien m…ô yakamni n…ôgkiarien m…®n…ô e tuk n…ôtap…®gien k…®n n…ôgkiarien kape narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhani hah …ômaw…ô. M…ôr…®g ye n…®mr…® Kughen, yakamni …ôm…ô n…ôgkiarien yame Kristo rorkeikei. K…®ni yo m…®n…ô t…®ks…®n, norien m-fam yame yakasor, yakasor m…ô k…®mi…ô takhaskai.  
