\v 21 Yakp…ôh norkeikeiyen m…ô n…®p…®g jakur…ô, kafak Kughen tukror yaur…®s yo, r…®kik r…ômh…ô, yakas…ôk, meinai k…®mi…ô t…®ks…®n nakw…ôsor t…ôvhag…ô has, masor apnap…®g nar, mamhak…®r ap…®s-ap…®s …ômi…ô m…®n…ô, mhap…ôh han…ô n…®sararien ye n…ôt…ôr…®gien kap…ômi…ô.\x - \xo 12:21 \xt 2 Kor 13:2 \x*   
\c 13  
\s1 Pol ramor kwir…®g k…®mi …ôri…ô  
\p
\v 1 In e n…®p…®g yame ror k…®sis…ôr k…®n yame jakur…ô m…ôm …ômi…ô. N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen ramni m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô yermam…ô k…®raru u…ô k…®sis…ôr k…®rh…®ni n…ôgkiarien k…®rikian…ô, p…ôh narmam…ô tukharkun m…ô n…ôgkiarien kap…ôris…®r ram…ôfrak…®s.‚Äù\rq (Dut 19:15)\rq*\f + \fr 13:1 \ft  N…ôgkiarien e ram…ôm…®r ye Dut 19:15. N…®pran e ramni m…ô n…ôkw…ôkw…ô k…®raru u…ô k…®sis…ôr yam…ô m…®ne Pol r…®m…®rai ramv…ôn k…®mi nim…ôhuak apa Korin, kap…ôri…ô n…ôgkiarien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô, ror p…ôn, kas…ôfrak…®s.\f*\x - \xo 13:1 \xt Mat 18:16; 1 Tim 5:19 \x*  
\v 2 N…®p…®g y…®mnaur…ô tuk …ômi…ô, ye n…®p…®g yame ror k…®raru k…®n, y…®m…®ni-…ôrhav pre ta n…ôgkiarien kape n…®s…®gien narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kasor t…ôvhag…ô has m…®ne …ômi…ô m-fam, m…ô taks…ôp…ôh t…ôvhag…ô hah. K…®ni yakam…ôm…®r isok mamni-pre m…®n. N…®p…®g jakur…ô m…®n, jakv…ôhsi-p…ôn narp…®nien k…®mi narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne khap…ôh n…®s…ôp…ôhyen norien has m…®n…ô.  
\v 3 K…®mi…ô nakham…ô t…ôks…ôkir …ômhen m…ô n…ôgkiarien kafak in n…ôgkiarien kape Kristo u…ô n…®kam. K…®ni yo jak…ôgkiar r…ômhen k…®n aposol k…®rik kafan. Norien kafan r…®p…ôh n…®marien tuk …ômi…ô, m…ôr…®g norien kafan r…®skai tuk …ômi…ô.  
