\v 7 K…®ni takt…ôkun ai, yaks…ôhuak tuk …ômi…ô m…ô takhap…ôh n…®sorien nar has m…®n…ô. M…ôr…®g r…®p…ôh norien m…ô yakas…ôhuak m…ôknak…®n m…ô tukramhajoun m…ô kap…ômaw…ô wok in rhuv…ô matuatuk. M…ôr…®g yakas…ôhuak m…ôknak…®n meinai yaksorkeikei m…ô taksor norien yame ratuatuk, nar apnap…®g m…ô narmam…ô kamhani m…ô wok kap…ômaw…ô r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien.  
\v 8 Tukm…ô nakhap…ôh n…®sorien t…ôvhag…ô hah, to yakhap…ôh n…®s…ôgkiar-skai-preyen k…®mi …ômi…ô, meinai yakseinein n…®sorien nar k…®rik yame ram…ôtap…®g k…®n n…ôgkiarien …ôfrak…®s kape Kughen, m…ôr…®g yakharkun n…®sor-…ôm…ôyen nar yame rav…ôhsi-hakt…ô n…ôgkiarien …ôfrak…®s kape Kughen.  
